{"type":"weapons","title":"Blade of Grass","summaries":["The <b>Blade of Grass</b> is a <linked>broadsword</linked> crafted using materials from the <linked>Underground Jungle</linked>. It has a decent size and swing reach, and has a 25% chance of inflicting the <linked>Poisoned</linked> <linked>debuff</linked> for 7 seconds upon striking enemies. It is also one of the key ingredients in crafting the <linked>Night's Edge</linked>.","On the <linked>[img:Desktop version]</linked><linked> Desktop version</linked>, <linked>[img:Console version]</linked><linked> Console version</linked>, and <linked>[img:Mobile version]</linked><linked> Mobile version</linked>, Blade of Grass is roughly equal to the <linked>Volcano</linked> in size, making it one of the largest swords in <linked>Pre-Hardmode</linked>. When swung, it fires a small, green Leaf Blade projectile that flies upwards in a circle, leaving behind a green particle effect resembling leaves. The Leaf Blade projectile has 20 <linked>armor penetration</linked>, can automatically target enemies within a radius of 9.375 tiles, deals 25% base damage (4 base damage), 100% knockback (4.5 <span class=\"knockback\">(Average)</span>), and has the same chance to inflict Poisoned for the same duration as the sword itself.","Its best <linked>modifier</linked> is <b>Legendary</b>."],"statistics":{"Damage":"18 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 28 <span class=\"eico s i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"small-bold\">(Melee)</span>","Knockback":"4.5 <span class=\"knockback\">(Average)</span> <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 3 <span class=\"knockback\">(Very weak)</span> <span class=\"eico s i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Critical chance":"4%","Use time":"20 <s